Var. glaucescens MALME.

X. ylaucescens MALME, in anmz, Repert. spec. nov. V (1908), p. 102.

Folia glaucescentia, ensiformi-linearia, 10-15 cm, rarius usque 18 cm longa, 3—4 mm lata, oblique acuminata, utraque acie laevigata, ceterum subtiliter transverse rugulosa, minus distincte nervoso—striata, vagina tertiam fere partem folii occupante, superne lamina paullulo angustiore, ligula acuta munita, stramineo-fulvescente v. fulvo-ferruginea, opaca, om- nino eciliata. Scapi superne compressi et bicostat-i, 25—40 cm alti, 1—1‚25 mm lati, in costis scabriduli, ceterum superne sublaevigati‚ vagina basali 8—-10 cm longa, in apiculum bre- vem, acuminatum excurrente, inferne ferrugineo-castanea, laevi (haud tuberculata), opaca. Spica obovoidea, 8—10 mm longa, circiter 5 mm crassa, bracteae infimae late ellipticae‚ circiter 4 mm longae, intermediae ovales, 7—8 mm longae, 4—4,.5 mm latae, apice rotundatae V. obtusissimae, avellaneo— fulvescentes v. dilute ferrugineo-fulvae, subopacae, fere inte- gerrimae, sub apice obtuse carinatae, area dorsali ovato—lanceo- lata, circiter 4 mm longa.
